cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IT, cs.NA, cs.SI 

This paper deals with optimization of energy functionals in image analysis problems, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also introduces an efficient convex optimization algorithm based on the alternating direction method of multipliers (ADMM), which falls under the category of numerical analysis (cs.NA). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of a Huber loss function, which is a common topic in signal processing (cs.IT) and statistics (cs.SI).
